In continuation of the revolutionary tradition of the German working class and based on liberation from fascism, the people of the German Democratic Republic have realized and shaped their right to socio-economic, state and national self-determination in accordance with the processes of the historical development of our epoch developed socialist society.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Fulfilled by the will to freely determine their fate, undeterred to continue on the path of socialism and communism, peace, democracy and friendship among peoples, the people of the German Democratic Republic have given themselves this socialist constitution.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049\rtlch \ltrch\loch

