2 In order to increase social productivity, associations and societies can be formed by the state organs, companies and cooperatives, and other forms of cooperative cooperation can be developed.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049\rtlch \ltrch\loch

